{"type":"answer","id":119085,"parentType":"question","parentId":1115,"uid":9304,"contents":"大奸大恶，邪教头目<br>\n党文化不但在纵向割断了中华民族祖辈承传的智慧，同时也在横向以敌视的态度对待西方的优秀文明。这就使得受其熏陶的中国人只能相信党文化中的“枪杆子里面出政权”，“机关枪、大炮是最有权威的东西”（恩格斯），“物质力量只能用物质力量摧毁”（马克思）。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ENNDTJTXUAAr07z?format=png&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ENNDTJTXUAAr07z?format=png&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ENNDTJTXUAAr07z?format=png&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-02","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}